      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it honestly still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect and ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Let's get you in the driver's seat!",
