    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a turn-key E46 M3 in museum-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a recent comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the precise turn-in and feedback these cars are famed for. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage and flawless factory paint depth. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
